        "timestamp": "2017-08-28 21:37:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nI would much prefer to see this additional docker integrated into the docker-compose script so all the containers can be managed with a single command.  Is this feasible?",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "21f15ab80cfbf3e033d01e673212b3ff380074e2",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 741,
          "name": "Kanagaraj Manickam",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "kanagaraj.manickam@huawei.com",
          "username": "mkr1481"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-08-29 04:10:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nDear Chris, CLI project is different that the portal project, and I think its not an good idea to add CLI into the portal project repository. (docker compose files for portal is under portal project.)\n\nbut at the same time, we don't want to spare separate VM for CLI in this release. so we have added CLI deployment as part of the Portal VM. \n\nHope this would answered your queries. please let me know if you need any other details. thanks.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "27a9627d98a5ae637c0fd9dffae0273e484073e1",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 681,
          "name": "Chris Lott",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "cl778h@att.com",
          "username": "cl778h"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-08-29 17:34:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: -Code-Review\n\nOk I see the point about keeping the CLI docker separate from the Portal docker details.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "76db283e639115a95bf4d6ed6190bb20275ab1e3",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 681,
          "name": "Chris Lott",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "cl778h@att.com",
          "username": "cl778h"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-08-29 21:04:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nDo you know about the OOM-based deployment effort lead by Mike Elliott and David Sauvageau?  That will replace our little docker-compose solution entirely.  If you want this CLI in the R1 release I suggest coordinating with them at your earliest convenience.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
