        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-01 10:30:35.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nSo, I still see a problem here.  There are two steps required in Rackspace:\n(1) Pull the image so the local docker engine has it (portal_vm_init.sh)\n(2) Create a container from a local image (docker-compose.yml)\nYou have modified the docker-compose.yml (via .env file), but it will not work until step (1) establishes the precondition by pulling that image.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "869c735a2b24f6c2cac9d21195eb51a6a45c143e",
        "author": {
