        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-04 05:39:30.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nDear Chris, thanks for pointing out. Now I have increased the version to 1.1 to make it simple. once its available as part of todays daily build, i believe things should be working properly. please let me know if any other changes to be done. thanks.",
